cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language generation models. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel reward function for reinforcement learning. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with improving language generation models using machine learning techniques. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it proposes a new reward function for neural networks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as headline generation is often used in image captioning tasks.
